1982;;After the Axe;;Canadian;;Sturla Gunnarsson;;James Douglas;;national film board docudrama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/After_the_Axe;;Wilson, a senior marketing executive, is laid off from a food company after fifteen years of good service. Losing his status and security, he is relegated to the role of dependent house husband, resented by his children and shunned by former colleagues.[3]